Revision history for nginx-auth-saslauthd

1.000  2019-09-15 09:10:48 CET

  - Check whether there's a reply from the saslauthd.

0.008  2018-11-08 11:05:38 CET

  - Reject empty passwords and login names.

0.007  2018-09-25 23:28:47 CEST

  - Support Latin-1 encoded credentials.

0.006  2018-09-18 04:04:12 CEST

  - Read the configuration from /etc/nginx/auth-saslauthd.conf.

0.005  2017-11-25 12:16:09 CET

  - Prepare for a possible CPAN release.

0.004  2017-11-14 05:30:30 CET

  - Accumulate the saslauthd daemon's reply.

0.003  2017-11-08 07:49:29 CET

  - Ask the client to encode the credentials in UTF-8.
  - Encode the SASL realm and service in UTF-8.
  - The realm for Basic authentication must only contain ASCII characters.

0.002  2017-11-07 09:12:36 CET

  - Check whether the HTTP connection has been closed early.
  - Raise the default saslauthd timeout from 5 to 10 seconds.

0.001  2017-11-05 18:59:51 CET

  - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

